one_reviews_text: You can set up crates on chairs, stools, and barrels and shoot em off which is fun, and you can shoot the punching bag and do alot of fun stuff. Id like to see more guns added and more crates and barrels

Huge 'pranos' fan here... #1 show in television history... this is cool, & free... a few more details and a little more time on layout coulda crushed this... Also, would be a great spot for virtual meetings... If I could negotiate with people sitting behind Tony's desk...

For the 15 seconds I was in the game it seemed small, not much to do and not much to look at. It seemed that it would entertain me for about 15 minutes before i'd get bored. After 15 seconds the game crashed. I thought that i could just reboot the game but error messeges keppt showing up.

Was a fun and FREE little game. I see good potential with it and hope it keeps going I think will get very popular. I know this is very lame but first thing i did was grab a beer and try to drink it. Should add effects and sound like PokerstarsVR or Drunkn Bar Fight. I am going to be sure to keep a eye on this one looks to be great game.

review_title: Great place to chillout for 5 minutes
one_reviews_text: Really neat stuff goin on, although I do wish there was just a tiny bit more, but great place to just relax and have a bit of fun.

A nice place to chill out for 15 minutes. You can throw some dice, play chess, shoot bottles, throw darts. My only gripes are that the friction on the pool table is too high, and I didn't seem to be able to throw small things (like darts and chess pieces) as far as I expected.
review_feedback: Thanks for your feedback. Well seen. These things are on my to-do list to improve.

one_reviews_text: This would not work at all for me, and I don't know why. So, I uninstalled it. A total waste of space and time!
review_feedback: Thanks for your feedback. We regret for the problems you had. If you wish, we would be pleased if you could give us more information about the specific problem you had. I leave you a link to our support page. https://forms.gle/Ci8fnW3rvJfG1XTs7
